      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this constant loop. every time i think i finally figured things out or got a grip on my life, i just end up right back where i started. same mistakes, same failures, same emptiness. it feels like no matter what i do, the outcome is always gonna be the same. it's just exhausting.",
