    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like \"releasing the pressure\" isn't enough. i've tried letting things settle, i've tried walking away, i've tried everything. it's like a glitch in a program where no matter what input you give it, the error stays the same. i'm just so tired of fighting a battle that's already been lost. there's no version of the future where this isn't happening again.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
